properties.areaDesc: Nantucket Sound; Massachusetts Bay and Ipswich Bay; Cape Cod Bay
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 15 at 3:26AM EST until January 17 at 1:00PM EST by NWS Boston/Norton MA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northwest winds 20 to 30 kt with gusts up to 45 kt and
seas 5 to 8 feet expected.

* WHERE...Cape Cod Bay, Nantucket Sound and Massachusetts Bay
and Ipswich Bay.

* WHEN...From 6 AM Thursday to 1 PM EST Friday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous seas which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 6 AM THURSDAY TO 1 PM EST FRIDAY
